imdb.plot outline: Who has the right stuff? Discovery takes audiences into the fun and far reaches of science and technology with this world premiere competition series. Top Engineer searches for America's brightest, boldest, out-of-the-box thinkers and pits them against one another. With innovative solution to the challenges they are tasked with, competing teams are sure to blow minds as well as a few other things along the way.
